Interface Array_ListOfInteger_Interface

All Superinterfaces:
ListOfInteger_Interface
All Known Implementing Classes:
Array_ListOfInteger
public interface Array_ListOfInteger_Interface extends ListOfInteger_Interface
Adds methods related to capacity, which are required for an array list. Notes about capacity:
  • When adding an element, if size == capacity the capacity is doubled
  • When removing an element, the capacity is not changed
  • The clear method does not change the capacity
Author:
Kevin Lillis
